{"tid":2512273,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"男警墮網上情緣騙局被騙20萬 網交女友稱因疫情滯日本索錢應急","createTime":"2021-05-01T14:20:18.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-01T14:36:48.000Z","uid":50386,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"a57a1687eb47429c900423bae40fdd756c39355a","tid":2512273,"uid":50386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T14:20:18.000Z","msg":"一名22歲警員近日墮入網上情緣騙案，他早前在交友程式認識一名女子後，對方訛稱因疫情滯留日本，急需金錢應急。男警匯款20萬予對方後，對方近日失去聯絡，男警昨日（4月30日）報警求助<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n據了解，事主為一名22歲男警員，駐守長沙灣警署。據悉他去年12月在交友程式結識一名女子，二人交談甚歡，迅速發展成男女朋友關係，惟雙方未曾見面。女子訛稱自己因疫情滯留日本，積蓄快要用完，要求男警匯款給她應付日常開支。男警不虞有詐，先後匯款20萬元給對方。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n該女子近日失聯，男警發現被騙，<strong><span class=\"red\">遂通知上級，上級著他到就近警署報案。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20210501/s00001/1619876442164/網交女友稱因疫情滯日本索錢應急-男警墮網上情緣騙局被騙20萬\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20210501%2Fs00001%2F1619876442164%2F%E7%B6%B2%E4%BA%A4%E5%A5%B3%E5%8F%8B%E7%A8%B1%E5%9B%A0%E7%96%AB%E6%83%85%E6%BB%AF%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E7%B4%A2%E9%8C%A2%E6%87%89%E6%80%A5-%E7%94%B7%E8%AD%A6%E5%A2%AE%E7%B6%B2%E4%B8%8A%E6%83%85%E7%B7%A3%E9%A8%99%E5%B1%80%E8%A2%AB%E9%A8%9920%E8%90%AC&d=Z1ElB6oaYTZYlgUQOIdQNpggdM0W6%2BkgeusliPwa7Y4%3D&h=5982e097\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20210501%2Fs00001%2F1619876442164%2F%E7%B6%B2%E4%BA%A4%E5%A5%B3%E5%8F%8B%E7%A8%B1%E5%9B%A0%E7%96%AB%E6%83%85%E6%BB%AF%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E7%B4%A2%E9%8C%A2%E6%87%89%E6%80%A5-%E7%94%B7%E8%AD%A6%E5%A2%AE%E7%B6%B2%E4%B8%8A%E6%83%85%E7%B7%A3%E9%A8%99%E5%B1%80%E8%A2%AB%E9%A8%9920%E8%90%AC&h=7a7ed41e\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20210501/s00001/1619876442164/網交女友稱因疫情滯日本索錢應急-男警墮網上情緣騙局被騙20萬</a><br />\n毅進狗果然係毅進狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea4489ed2f99feec56b8f408a3ea89623bfad654","tid":2512273,"uid":393145,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T14:22:34.000Z","msg":"警察自己報警都要人教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1aa08f073060b0dc046a4159aea8468a94c30903","tid":2512273,"uid":78243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T14:30:39.000Z","msg":"啲警察真係好撚蠢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02df2f2701b45d8fe1bdf8fb65dcfbf2539cfb29","tid":2512273,"uid":330728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T14:36:48.000Z","msg":"去附近警署報案"}]}